WEBVTT

00:22.190 --> 00:23.050
Have you got it?

00:23.600 --> 00:24.200
Of course.

00:24.250 --> 00:26.190
I'm the Reception Envoy
appointed by my father.

00:26.190 --> 00:27.640
They would naturally give me the pass.

00:27.640 --> 00:28.230
Good.

00:28.480 --> 00:29.830
Then let's depart immediately.

00:29.830 --> 00:32.159
Go 30 li east
and then switch to waterways.

00:32.320 --> 00:34.590
We should be able to reach
Qingluan Pass within 5 days.

00:34.590 --> 00:35.710
Once at Qingluan Pass,

00:35.710 --> 00:36.670
take Xiao Ran and the others

00:36.670 --> 00:38.400
and continue east to Lincheng.

00:38.640 --> 00:40.430
The rest of the envoy team turns south

00:40.430 --> 00:41.600
and heads to Qiongzhou.

00:41.600 --> 00:44.390
Guide Envoy Lord Zhan Ziyu has arrived.

00:49.530 --> 00:50.330
Leave it to me.

01:02.000 --> 01:03.240
Your Highness.

01:03.750 --> 01:07.200
Her Majesty heard that you're going
to Qiongzhou with King Ximeng.

01:07.200 --> 01:10.150
You hurriedly got the imperial pass
from the Ministry of Rites yesterday.

01:10.150 --> 01:11.870
I didn't expect you to leave today.

01:11.870 --> 01:15.070
I wonder why you're in such a hurry.

01:15.430 --> 01:17.560
What are you talking about, Lord Zhan?

01:17.560 --> 01:19.280
My royal parents gave me the grace

01:19.280 --> 01:20.789
to be the Reception Envoy

01:21.039 --> 01:23.039
and accompany King Ximeng on a tour.

01:23.070 --> 01:24.560
How dare I slack off?

01:24.840 --> 01:27.170
Your Highness, you're absolutely right.

01:27.480 --> 01:29.680
But I find it very strange.

01:31.200 --> 01:32.660
Qiongzhou is a long way off

01:32.750 --> 01:34.759
and has no scenery.

01:34.950 --> 01:36.590
King Ximeng came from afar,

01:38.680 --> 01:41.920
so he should enjoy
the beautiful scenery of Biantang.

01:42.070 --> 01:44.560
Why go all the way to Qiongzhou?

01:44.950 --> 01:45.840
Could it be...

01:47.479 --> 01:50.310
that there is something special
about Qiongzhou?

01:52.150 --> 01:53.640
Don't ask, Lord Zhan.

01:54.780 --> 01:56.580
I'm wondering too.

01:56.920 --> 01:58.759
This old man from Ximeng is very weird.

01:58.759 --> 02:01.070
He insists on going
to that damn Qiongzhou.

02:01.070 --> 02:02.280
I'm very reluctant.

02:02.280 --> 02:04.210
How did I end up with such a hard job?

02:05.840 --> 02:07.900
Why speak such words, Your Highness?

02:08.289 --> 02:10.320
Her Majesty has always loved you the most.

02:10.320 --> 02:12.320
To show sympathy for your hard work,

02:12.320 --> 02:14.640
she specially sent me as a Guide Envoy

02:15.240 --> 02:16.100
to clear the way

02:16.750 --> 02:18.800
for you and King Ximeng.

02:19.470 --> 02:20.840
That's not necessary.

02:20.840 --> 02:22.120
Going to Qiongzhou is a trivial matter.

02:22.120 --> 02:23.520
How can I bother you, Lord Zhan?

02:23.520 --> 02:25.180
You are wrong, Your Highness.

02:26.400 --> 02:29.150
Receiving foreigners
is an important matter for the country.

02:29.150 --> 02:31.430
How can you say it's a trivial matter?

02:31.590 --> 02:32.520
What's more,

02:33.800 --> 02:35.870
this is Her Majesty's decree.

02:36.680 --> 02:38.150
Let alone me,

02:39.260 --> 02:40.350
even you

02:40.430 --> 02:42.630
should follow it carefully.

02:50.150 --> 02:51.150
Your Highness.

02:51.710 --> 02:54.280
Since Lord Zhan has conveyed
Her Majesty's gracious intention,

02:54.280 --> 02:56.200
I can't naturally disappoint him.

02:56.200 --> 02:57.560
Let's travel

02:57.560 --> 02:58.680
with Lord Zhan.

04:23.770 --> 04:29.310
[REBIRTH]

04:29.850 --> 04:32.180
[Episode 14]

04:48.490 --> 04:52.440
[Qingluan Pass]

04:56.920 --> 04:57.720
Your Highness,

04:57.720 --> 04:59.390
we have arrived at Qingluan Pass.

04:59.390 --> 05:00.560
There are 2 forks ahead.

05:00.560 --> 05:01.950
One to the east and one to the west.

05:01.950 --> 05:03.870
Both can reach Qiongzhou Prefecture.

05:03.870 --> 05:05.510
Go east. Set off immediately.

05:05.510 --> 05:06.800
Wait, Your Highness.

05:07.480 --> 05:09.210
To go to Qiongzhou Prefecture,

05:09.240 --> 05:10.720
you should head west.

05:11.310 --> 05:12.870
The terrain in the east is steep,

05:12.870 --> 05:14.430
with many mountains and wild beasts.

05:14.430 --> 05:16.030
The west is an official road.

05:16.120 --> 05:17.480
There are post stations along the way,

05:17.480 --> 05:19.210
which is much more convenient.

05:19.720 --> 05:21.650
The road in the east is a bit rugged,

05:21.720 --> 05:23.060
but there are shortcuts.

05:23.060 --> 05:25.720
We can arrive
at Qiongzhou Prefecture earlier.

05:25.830 --> 05:26.950
That's strange.

05:27.360 --> 05:29.000
You don't take the flat official road

05:29.000 --> 05:30.190
in the west,

05:30.270 --> 05:31.600
but insists on going
to the deserted, dangerous mountains

05:31.600 --> 05:33.000
in the east.

05:33.240 --> 05:34.390
Could it be that the east

05:34.390 --> 05:36.190
has something special?

05:36.870 --> 05:37.480
Or is it that King Ximeng

05:37.480 --> 05:40.000
and you have ulterior motives?

05:40.630 --> 05:41.390
You are not

05:41.720 --> 05:43.190
going to Qiongzhou at all,

05:43.920 --> 05:45.640
but somewhere else, are you?

05:47.680 --> 05:49.600
Lord Zhan, you're indeed smart.

05:50.000 --> 05:50.870
You can tell at a glance

05:50.870 --> 05:52.530
that I have ulterior motives.

05:52.680 --> 05:54.040
To tell you the truth, Lord Zhan,

05:54.040 --> 05:57.060
it's said that heading east
from here will pass by Yingchuan.

05:57.060 --> 05:58.800
There is not only good wine and food

05:58.800 --> 06:00.460
but also countless beauties.

06:01.240 --> 06:02.860
I do have some selfish motives

06:02.860 --> 06:04.320
and want to experience it.

06:04.430 --> 06:06.160
But since you're the Guide Envoy,

06:06.160 --> 06:07.830
I will listen to you.

06:08.270 --> 06:09.470
By Lord Zhan's order,

06:09.510 --> 06:11.440
take the official road in the west.

06:12.070 --> 06:13.000
I'm tired.

06:13.270 --> 06:15.130
Let's rest at the pavilion ahead.

06:26.920 --> 06:27.720
Attendant,

06:28.310 --> 06:29.190
come here.

06:44.950 --> 06:45.750
Your Majesty,

06:45.920 --> 06:47.120
what are your orders?

06:47.390 --> 06:48.560
It's cold.

06:48.920 --> 06:50.720
Go get me a blanket.

06:51.360 --> 06:51.920
Yes.

06:53.040 --> 06:53.600
Wait.

06:54.190 --> 06:55.190
Step forward.

06:59.600 --> 07:00.600
Hold your horses.

07:00.830 --> 07:01.510
Tonight, we will rest

07:01.510 --> 07:04.120
at the official post station
at Tianshui Ferry.

07:04.120 --> 07:05.470
We'll travel at night.

07:06.200 --> 07:08.230
So we can arrive
the night before Great Yong

07:08.230 --> 07:10.430
and Great Yan exchange their prisoners.

07:10.430 --> 07:11.040
Yes.

07:11.560 --> 07:13.600
Your Majesty, do you have anything else?

07:13.600 --> 07:14.630
If not,

07:14.870 --> 07:16.190
I will take my leave.

07:24.990 --> 07:25.670
My Lord.

07:26.120 --> 07:29.600
Keep an eye on
King Ximeng's personal guards.

07:30.240 --> 07:32.040
See if you can

07:32.680 --> 07:34.080
find any clues from them.

07:35.070 --> 07:35.600
Yes.

07:50.430 --> 07:51.830
Welcome, Your Highness.

08:13.630 --> 08:14.190
Come on.

08:15.120 --> 08:16.270
Delicious, delicious.

08:16.270 --> 08:17.600
This is also delicious.

08:18.270 --> 08:18.870
I need more.

08:18.870 --> 08:19.800
Come on, come on.

08:20.760 --> 08:22.020
Eat some meat. Come on.

08:24.190 --> 08:25.160
Come on. Eat some meat.

08:25.160 --> 08:25.720
Eat some meat.

08:25.720 --> 08:27.120
The meat is so delicious.

08:28.210 --> 08:29.540
Delicious, delicious.

08:30.040 --> 08:31.370
This meat is delicious.

08:32.929 --> 08:34.270
Meat is much better.

08:35.270 --> 08:36.720
Come on, eat.

08:36.750 --> 08:37.669
Come on, come on.

08:37.669 --> 08:39.070
-Eat the meat.
-Eat, eat.

08:42.549 --> 08:43.549
Where's the wine?

08:44.030 --> 08:44.910
Why do we get to eat

08:44.910 --> 08:46.440
dry rations and cabbage,

08:47.000 --> 08:48.550
while they get to eat a sumptuous meal

08:48.550 --> 08:49.550
with delicacies?

08:52.600 --> 08:54.200
Why do we get to eat this?

08:54.950 --> 08:56.030
We want meat!

08:56.240 --> 08:57.200
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

08:57.200 --> 08:58.360
-We want meat!
-We want meat!

08:58.360 --> 08:59.870
Come on, eat the meat!

09:01.750 --> 09:02.630
Come on, drink!

09:02.800 --> 09:03.680
Sirs,

09:03.710 --> 09:05.790
I'm really sorry for the poor service.

09:05.790 --> 09:07.150
You may not know this,

09:07.150 --> 09:10.630
but it has been pouring rain for days,

09:11.030 --> 09:13.120
and there are flash floods.

09:13.870 --> 09:15.750
The merchants
transporting fresh vegetables

09:15.750 --> 09:18.200
and meat to the post station
have been delayed.

09:18.200 --> 09:21.390
So right now,
there's not enough food here.

09:21.680 --> 09:24.000
I really can't arrange it.

09:29.390 --> 09:30.910
-Sir, Sir!
-You think we can be fooled?

09:30.910 --> 09:32.150
Not enough food?

09:32.960 --> 09:35.020
Why do they get to eat a sumptuous meal

09:35.270 --> 09:37.080
with delicacies?

09:41.390 --> 09:43.080
Calm down, Sirs, please!

09:43.440 --> 09:45.360
Lord Zhan arranged it this way.

09:45.360 --> 09:47.670
I'm just following orders.

09:47.670 --> 09:49.790
Please be understanding.

09:49.960 --> 09:52.360
A sumptuous meal!

09:53.240 --> 09:54.700
-Delicious!
-Delicious!

09:55.120 --> 09:57.480
-With delicacies!
-With delicacies!

09:57.480 --> 09:58.840
-Fresh!
-Fresh!

09:59.360 --> 10:00.610
Sirs, you can't!

10:00.630 --> 10:01.750
You can't!

10:01.750 --> 10:02.200
Sirs!

10:02.200 --> 10:02.910
Come on!

10:04.200 --> 10:07.510
A sumptuous meal is bad for your health.

10:08.310 --> 10:09.040
Yeah, yeah.

10:09.550 --> 10:13.000
Simple fare is good
for your health instead.

10:13.510 --> 10:14.350
Yeah, yeah.

10:14.790 --> 10:15.770
Let's go, come on.

10:15.770 --> 10:16.700
Come on, come on.

10:20.840 --> 10:22.510
Simple fare,

10:22.840 --> 10:24.390
-good health.
-good health.

10:24.390 --> 10:25.570
A sumptuous meal,

10:26.240 --> 10:28.240
-choke to death!
-choke to death!

10:28.440 --> 10:29.000
Eat.

10:29.440 --> 10:30.510
Eat. Let's eat ours.

10:30.510 --> 10:31.840
Come on, let's eat ours.

10:35.550 --> 10:36.390
What are you waiting for?

10:36.390 --> 10:37.320
Eat and drink.

10:54.050 --> 10:54.770
Let me see.

10:55.690 --> 10:56.330
Nothing.

10:58.600 --> 10:59.800
What is all this junk?

11:03.200 --> 11:04.120
What did you do?

11:06.720 --> 11:08.600
Why did you go through our bags?

11:09.170 --> 11:12.170
Which eye saw us going through them?

11:12.200 --> 11:14.000
Yeah, which eye?

11:15.200 --> 11:16.440
You Ximeng people

11:16.710 --> 11:18.390
are just like these beasts of burden,

11:18.390 --> 11:19.450
poor and backward.

11:19.550 --> 11:20.270
Tell me,

11:20.440 --> 11:22.030
with your ragged bags,

11:22.240 --> 11:23.770
what's there to go through?

11:26.500 --> 11:27.630
Useless fool!

11:48.960 --> 11:50.030
So it...

11:50.510 --> 11:52.510
-is a little girl!
-is a little girl!

11:54.270 --> 11:55.000
How dare you!

11:55.390 --> 11:56.450
What are you doing?

12:02.270 --> 12:03.200
What's going on?

12:03.390 --> 12:04.680
Lord Zhan, it is a—

12:04.790 --> 12:06.010
Lord Zhan, it is—

12:09.240 --> 12:10.640
Lord Zhan, it is a little—

12:23.080 --> 12:24.030
Lord Zhan.

12:24.910 --> 12:26.720
You received Her Majesty's decree

12:26.720 --> 12:28.720
to serve as the Guide Envoy for Ximeng,

12:28.720 --> 12:30.830
yet you mistreated
Ximeng's soldiers like this,

12:30.830 --> 12:33.270
damaging the relation
between Biantang and Ximeng.

12:33.270 --> 12:34.340
Acting like this,

12:34.440 --> 12:36.840
aren't you afraid
my mother will blame you?

12:37.200 --> 12:39.910
Seems you're in a bad mood today,
Your Highness.

12:40.670 --> 12:42.000
You reminded me

12:42.000 --> 12:44.080
that damaging the relation
between Ximeng and Biantang

12:44.080 --> 12:45.940
might incur Her Majesty's wrath.

12:46.420 --> 12:47.970
But I feel that

12:48.840 --> 12:50.550
you indiscriminately

12:50.550 --> 12:52.320
killed Biantang's soldiers,

12:52.670 --> 12:54.930
and it will enrage Her Majesty even more.

12:55.340 --> 12:56.850
Your Highness, do not forget one thing.

12:56.850 --> 12:58.780
The reason Her Majesty sent me here

12:58.790 --> 13:00.150
is to prevent the Crown Prince

13:00.150 --> 13:04.270
from doing absurd things
that disgrace Biantang.

13:04.910 --> 13:05.740
Lord Zhan.

13:12.120 --> 13:13.550
I only killed

13:13.550 --> 13:15.120
2 troublemaking soldiers.

13:16.120 --> 13:19.550
I didn't kill the Ceremonial Officer
and Guide Envoy, Lord Zhan.

13:19.550 --> 13:21.480
How would that disgrace Biantang?

13:27.790 --> 13:28.510
Why?

13:29.670 --> 13:31.250
Lord Zhan, are you afraid?

13:31.460 --> 13:33.070
It seems you remember

13:33.480 --> 13:35.610
that I am the Crown Prince of Biantang.

13:35.980 --> 13:36.730
And you,

13:37.630 --> 13:39.690
a Ceremonial Officer or Guide Envoy,

13:40.510 --> 13:41.510
in the end,

13:42.750 --> 13:44.550
are nothing but... but...

13:47.390 --> 13:48.700
a male favorite.

13:51.240 --> 13:52.100
Your Highness,

13:53.180 --> 13:54.820
whether I am a Guide Envoy

13:55.240 --> 13:56.550
or a male favorite,

13:56.910 --> 13:58.630
it's bestowed by Her Majesty.

13:59.030 --> 14:00.080
It's not your place to judge.

14:00.080 --> 14:01.670
But these troublemaking Biantang soldiers

14:01.670 --> 14:04.070
have already been killed
by your own hands.

14:06.200 --> 14:07.360
That Ximeng soldier

14:07.360 --> 14:10.200
should also be taken away and interrogated

14:11.800 --> 14:14.640
to find out what exactly is going on.

14:14.910 --> 14:15.550
Guards,

14:16.200 --> 14:17.600
arrest

14:17.600 --> 14:18.750
this troublemaking Ximeng soldier.

14:18.750 --> 14:19.410
-Yes.
-Yes.

14:22.150 --> 14:23.000
Hold on.

14:30.390 --> 14:31.320
Lord Zhan.

14:31.790 --> 14:33.790
Since the soldier under my command

14:33.810 --> 14:35.630
does not know Biantang's etiquette,

14:35.630 --> 14:37.750
just let me handle it.

14:38.750 --> 14:40.790
Take this troublemaker away

14:40.910 --> 14:42.550
and deal with him by military law.

14:42.550 --> 14:43.210
-Yes.
-Yes.

14:47.400 --> 14:48.080
Let go!

14:50.030 --> 14:50.630
Let go!

14:50.630 --> 14:51.510
Lord Zhan,

14:51.670 --> 14:53.200
am I not allowed

14:53.390 --> 14:55.080
to deal with my own soldier?

14:58.190 --> 14:58.910
Let go!

15:00.110 --> 15:00.780
Alright!

15:05.490 --> 15:06.090
Go.

15:06.340 --> 15:07.360
You just wait!

15:17.550 --> 15:18.550
The imperial map.

15:23.390 --> 15:24.450
The imperial pass.

15:31.200 --> 15:32.670
Traveling from Tangjing,

15:32.700 --> 15:34.360
we've already delayed
for a day on the road.

15:34.360 --> 15:35.960
Qingluan Pass is just ahead.

15:36.000 --> 15:36.960
You leave tonight.

15:36.960 --> 15:39.090
If you ride fast, you can still make it.

15:39.120 --> 15:40.720
Lincheng is an important pass
at the border

15:40.720 --> 15:41.790
of Great Yong and Great Yan

15:41.790 --> 15:43.910
and also an important military point
defended by Great Yong.

15:43.910 --> 15:44.720
The prisoner of war camp here

15:44.720 --> 15:46.840
holds important prisoners all year round.

15:46.840 --> 15:48.910
It might not be that easy
for you guys to succeed.

15:48.910 --> 15:49.910
Be very careful.

15:50.320 --> 15:51.000
I know.

15:53.630 --> 15:54.270
And,

15:55.240 --> 15:57.790
you don't have to return
the same way after rescuing He Xiao.

15:57.790 --> 16:00.030
You can circle back
to Biantang from the west.

16:00.030 --> 16:01.360
It'll be safer this way.

16:01.510 --> 16:02.480
According to the schedule,

16:02.480 --> 16:03.790
you should be able to arrive

16:03.790 --> 16:05.270
outside Tangjing in 15 days.

16:05.270 --> 16:07.670
Li Ce will arrange someone
to meet you then.

16:07.910 --> 16:08.630
Li Ce.

16:09.520 --> 16:11.510
You killed the guards sent by the Empress.

16:11.510 --> 16:13.750
You've already fallen out with Zhan Ziyu.

16:13.750 --> 16:15.200
He will definitely

16:15.200 --> 16:16.990
watch your every move in the future.

16:16.990 --> 16:19.520
It might be trouble
if you return to Biantang.

16:19.840 --> 16:20.790
My mother and I

16:21.150 --> 16:22.670
have actually known what kind of person

16:22.670 --> 16:24.150
each other is.

16:24.600 --> 16:26.960
We've just put on a fake show

16:26.960 --> 16:28.440
for over 10 years.

16:28.910 --> 16:30.030
She's prepared.

16:30.310 --> 16:31.070
So am I.

16:32.470 --> 16:33.120
Qiao,

16:33.950 --> 16:34.830
don't worry.

16:42.950 --> 16:45.160
[Ninghui Hall]

16:54.870 --> 16:56.240
Please inform His Majesty

16:56.240 --> 16:59.380
that Prince of Luo, Li Yan, and his future
Princess Consort, Zhao Chun'er,

16:59.380 --> 17:00.440
are here to seek an audience.

17:00.440 --> 17:01.640
His Majesty is asleep

17:01.790 --> 17:03.080
and hasn't left the bedchamber yet.

17:03.080 --> 17:04.740
It's inconvenient to report.

17:04.960 --> 17:06.440
It doesn't matter who you bring.

17:06.440 --> 17:07.700
You two just wait here.

17:22.720 --> 17:24.170
It's about to rain.

17:24.790 --> 17:26.650
How much longer do we have to wait?

17:28.349 --> 17:29.640
It shouldn't be too long.

17:29.640 --> 17:30.640
It's almost noon.

17:30.680 --> 17:32.480
His Majesty should wake up soon.

17:37.440 --> 17:38.240
Your Majesty,

17:38.920 --> 17:41.550
the Prince of Luo has brought his future
Princess Consort for an audience.

17:41.550 --> 17:42.840
They've been waiting outside the hall

17:42.840 --> 17:43.990
for a long time.

17:47.510 --> 17:48.400
Prince of Luo?

17:48.680 --> 17:51.140
When did I ever summon
his Princess Consort?

17:51.220 --> 17:51.830
Go.

17:52.350 --> 17:53.920
Go summon Beauty Han.

17:54.930 --> 17:55.520
Yes.

18:00.300 --> 18:01.060
Beauty Han,

18:01.080 --> 18:02.280
you are finally here.

18:02.400 --> 18:03.980
His Majesty has been talking about you
for the past two days.

18:03.980 --> 18:05.220
He missed you so much.

18:05.250 --> 18:06.460
His Majesty has been waiting
for you for a long time.

18:06.460 --> 18:07.720
Let's go into the hall.

18:24.360 --> 18:24.950
Chun'er,

18:25.490 --> 18:27.490
let's go wait out of the way for a bit.

18:30.510 --> 18:31.310
Wait!

18:36.720 --> 18:37.920
Where are you going?

18:38.160 --> 18:40.440
Didn't His Majesty tell you to wait here?

18:40.600 --> 18:42.190
Here means here.

18:42.640 --> 18:43.880
If you move,

18:44.350 --> 18:45.960
how can you call it here?

18:46.640 --> 18:47.510
Chief Fang,

18:48.310 --> 18:50.480
why must you make things difficult for us?

18:50.480 --> 18:52.350
Prince of Luo, what are you saying?

18:52.350 --> 18:53.440
I am but a servant.

18:53.640 --> 18:54.570
How would I dare?

18:57.300 --> 18:57.980
A vole!

18:58.000 --> 18:58.760
A vole!

18:59.330 --> 19:00.000
A vole!

19:00.030 --> 19:01.110
Quick! Catch it!

19:01.110 --> 19:02.720
Beauty Han is terrified of voles!

19:02.720 --> 19:03.270
Hurry!

19:04.930 --> 19:05.590
Where? I...

19:09.950 --> 19:10.560
Let's go.

19:13.460 --> 19:14.950
Chief Fang, are you okay?

19:28.360 --> 19:31.820
[Linrui Palace]

19:39.750 --> 19:40.440
Chun'er,

19:40.960 --> 19:42.360
why did you bring me here?

19:42.590 --> 19:44.240
Isn't this Her Majesty's bedchamber?

19:44.240 --> 19:45.720
We are not seeing His Majesty.

19:45.720 --> 19:47.350
We are going to see Her Majesty.

19:47.350 --> 19:49.420
Her Majesty is even less likely to see me.

19:49.420 --> 19:50.340
I have a plan.

20:02.070 --> 20:03.270
Please announce me.

20:03.880 --> 20:05.850
I'm the Princess Consort of Luo,
bestowed by Her Majesty.

20:05.850 --> 20:08.450
I have urgent matters
and must see Her Majesty.

20:12.110 --> 20:13.750
The Prince of Luo is not married yet.

20:13.750 --> 20:15.750
There is no Princess Consort of Luo.

20:17.300 --> 20:19.030
Give this to Her Majesty.

20:19.250 --> 20:20.290
She will see me.

20:30.440 --> 20:32.830
She says
she is the Princess Consort of Luo?

20:32.830 --> 20:33.550
Yes.

20:33.880 --> 20:35.610
She came with the Prince of Luo.

20:35.680 --> 20:37.140
They are waiting outside.

20:37.440 --> 20:38.770
Then tell her to come in.

20:39.000 --> 20:40.110
Just her.

20:40.720 --> 20:41.370
Yes.

20:46.640 --> 20:47.920
This jade pendant

20:47.920 --> 20:50.720
was a gift from Biantang

20:51.030 --> 20:53.680
when Noble Consort Wei
of Great Yong was pregnant.

20:53.680 --> 20:56.350
This is carved from Tianshan ice jade.

20:57.160 --> 20:58.620
It is extremely precious.

20:59.160 --> 21:01.070
I picked it myself.

21:01.440 --> 21:03.070
Since you have this jade,

21:03.240 --> 21:04.350
you must be...

21:06.320 --> 21:08.440
her executed daughter, right?

21:08.720 --> 21:10.920
Your Majesty, you're indeed very wise.

21:11.400 --> 21:12.460
My surname is Zhao,

21:12.590 --> 21:13.990
and my first name is Chun.

21:14.140 --> 21:16.040
I'm the daughter
of Noble Consort Wei of Great Yong.

21:16.040 --> 21:17.130
Zhao Chun'er.

21:18.110 --> 21:20.920
You said you are
my granted Princess Consort of Luo.

21:20.920 --> 21:21.990
What do you mean?

21:24.070 --> 21:25.930
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

21:26.240 --> 21:27.960
I took precautions for you

21:28.030 --> 21:29.230
and took the liberty.

21:29.680 --> 21:31.590
Please grant my wish, Your Majesty,

21:31.590 --> 21:33.550
and arrange a marriage
for the Prince of Luo and me.

21:33.550 --> 21:36.030
Although the Prince of Luo
has no power or influence,

21:36.030 --> 21:38.760
he's still a member
of the Biantang royal family.

21:39.110 --> 21:41.070
You are just a deposed princess,

21:41.300 --> 21:42.900
who is still guilty.

21:43.590 --> 21:44.960
Why do you think

21:45.440 --> 21:47.840
I would allow you
to marry the Prince of Luo?

21:47.880 --> 21:49.010
Because this matter

21:49.430 --> 21:50.860
is a win-win situation

21:51.310 --> 21:52.480
for both of us.

22:00.410 --> 22:02.170
I'd like to hear it.

22:03.270 --> 22:04.330
Stand up and speak.

22:10.440 --> 22:12.570
Three years ago, I offended my father,

22:12.930 --> 22:14.850
but now he is old and sick.

22:15.080 --> 22:16.830
Today in Great Yong, my brother,

22:16.830 --> 22:19.400
the Prince of Xiang, Zhao Che,
is in charge of the state.

22:19.400 --> 22:20.730
He holds military power

22:20.890 --> 22:22.400
and has the support of the people.

22:22.400 --> 22:24.600
He'll surely be Great Yong's next king.

22:25.240 --> 22:26.500
Although I am deposed,

22:26.830 --> 22:28.070
my brother Zhao Che

22:28.140 --> 22:29.670
has always loved me dearly.

22:30.500 --> 22:31.880
Before I came to Biantang,

22:31.880 --> 22:33.400
I had been living in the army.

22:33.400 --> 22:36.000
If you're willing to ignore my past

22:36.310 --> 22:38.310
and arrange a marriage
for the Prince of Luo and me,

22:38.310 --> 22:40.350
I can write to my brother.

22:41.250 --> 22:42.830
I will use this marriage as an excuse

22:42.830 --> 22:45.430
to beg him to restore
my identity as a princess.

22:47.960 --> 22:48.830
Why do you think

22:48.830 --> 22:51.050
the Prince of Xiang
will agree to your request?

22:51.050 --> 22:52.730
Just because he dotes on you?

22:56.720 --> 22:58.920
Your Majesty, you hold a high position.

22:59.110 --> 23:00.840
You should know better than me.

23:01.110 --> 23:03.310
A princess married to Biantang,

23:03.640 --> 23:05.720
compared to a dead deposed princess,

23:06.400 --> 23:08.460
is more beneficial to both Great Yong

23:08.920 --> 23:10.250
and the Prince of Xiang.

23:11.070 --> 23:12.480
For you,

23:13.750 --> 23:15.070
it should be the same.

23:41.880 --> 23:42.550
How is it?

23:43.310 --> 23:45.480
Her Majesty has arranged
a marriage for us.

23:45.480 --> 23:46.550
Really, Chun'er?

23:46.680 --> 23:48.940
It's scheduled for the 5th of next month.

23:49.270 --> 23:50.000
Great!

23:50.400 --> 23:51.400
Great, Chun'er!

24:08.480 --> 24:09.110
Princess,

24:09.750 --> 24:10.400
someone has been following us

24:10.400 --> 24:11.720
since last night.

24:12.070 --> 24:13.530
He's followed us for 40 li.

24:13.830 --> 24:14.590
I guess

24:14.750 --> 24:17.110
it's a tall young man,

24:17.750 --> 24:20.010
and his martial arts skills aren't weak.

24:20.310 --> 24:21.070
Ignore him.

24:27.960 --> 24:28.490
Let's go.

24:29.520 --> 24:31.250
Take a look. They are all fresh.

24:40.480 --> 24:42.810
Beyond the Baichuan River lies Lincheng.

24:42.880 --> 24:44.140
I see an inn over there.

24:44.480 --> 24:45.680
Why don't we stay here

24:45.790 --> 24:46.880
for the night?

25:02.270 --> 25:05.070
Sir, you wear a blue robe.
Might your surname be Xi?

25:05.830 --> 25:06.790
My surname is not Xi.

25:06.790 --> 25:09.440
A female guest said your surname is Xi.

25:09.830 --> 25:12.270
The appearance and temperament
she described

25:12.270 --> 25:14.000
are exactly like yours.

25:14.310 --> 25:17.070
Only the age doesn't match.

25:17.310 --> 25:19.310
She said it was an old man.

25:21.830 --> 25:22.630
That's right.

25:22.880 --> 25:23.880
I am the old man.

25:26.030 --> 25:27.230
What else did she say?

25:27.900 --> 25:29.860
She has already arranged

25:29.920 --> 25:31.240
your room and food.

25:31.440 --> 25:34.200
The room is a bit small,

25:35.110 --> 25:37.350
but she said you're old

25:37.350 --> 25:38.810
and have mobility issues,

25:39.030 --> 25:39.830
so she specifically informed me

25:39.830 --> 25:42.680
to tell you to be careful on the stairs.

25:44.240 --> 25:45.920
But you don't seem old to me.

25:46.110 --> 25:47.590
Then just follow her arrangements.

25:47.590 --> 25:49.270
Okay, please come this way.

25:55.220 --> 25:56.300
Sorry, Sir.

25:56.410 --> 25:59.500
The food was also arranged
by the female guest.

25:59.720 --> 26:02.440
She said you are over 60

26:02.490 --> 26:03.610
and have poor teeth,

26:03.610 --> 26:05.470
so you should have some porridge.

26:08.830 --> 26:09.720
Bring me a pot of aged wine.

26:09.720 --> 26:10.290
Okay.

26:10.920 --> 26:12.550
A pot of aged wine.

26:18.860 --> 26:21.690
With the continuous wars
between Great Yan and Great Yong,

26:21.690 --> 26:23.970
the leather business is getting harder.

26:24.000 --> 26:24.660
That's all.

26:25.200 --> 26:27.680
Just the transportation costs

26:28.240 --> 26:29.840
have multiplied several times.

26:29.840 --> 26:31.370
There's no money to be made.

26:32.920 --> 26:34.550
With the wars every year,

26:35.160 --> 26:37.680
my inn's business is also sluggish.

26:38.440 --> 26:39.240
You know what?

26:39.790 --> 26:41.640
Soon, Great Yan and Great Yong

26:41.640 --> 26:43.190
are going to exchange prisoners of war,

26:43.190 --> 26:46.250
so there are actually more travelers
passing through.

26:46.790 --> 26:48.240
Haven't Great Yong and Great Yan

26:48.240 --> 26:49.640
been at war all this time?

26:49.750 --> 26:51.130
Why are they suddenly exchanging prisoners

26:51.130 --> 26:52.450
at a time like this?

26:52.920 --> 26:54.590
It is said that among these prisoners

26:54.590 --> 26:56.160
are the former Xiuli Army.

26:56.240 --> 26:57.510
Chu Qiao has gone missing.

26:57.510 --> 26:59.110
In order to lure Chu Qiao out,

26:59.240 --> 27:00.830
the King of Great Yan is said
to be willing to do whatever it takes

27:00.830 --> 27:02.490
to exchange these prisoners.

27:02.750 --> 27:03.720
Have you heard?

27:03.720 --> 27:04.790
The King of Great Yan

27:04.790 --> 27:07.880
is considered a young warlord
dominating the region.

27:08.310 --> 27:10.200
But he is deeply in love

27:10.720 --> 27:12.960
with the female general Chu Qiao.

27:14.000 --> 27:14.790
That Chu Qiao

27:14.790 --> 27:17.320
was killed by Great Yong's
general Zhuge Yue.

27:18.620 --> 27:19.970
It is said that this Chu Qiao

27:19.970 --> 27:21.830
was once a female slave
of the Zhuge family.

27:21.830 --> 27:24.320
The Zhuge family
has kept slaves for generations.

27:24.320 --> 27:25.790
Especially this Zhuge Yue,

27:25.790 --> 27:27.680
who is the heir of their family.

27:28.350 --> 27:30.200
Who knows how many female slaves

27:30.200 --> 27:31.600
have been killed by them.

27:31.980 --> 27:33.690
Life and death are at others' mercy.

27:33.690 --> 27:34.890
How pathetic.

27:35.440 --> 27:37.200
But God has eyes.

27:37.370 --> 27:39.170
He also died in this frozen lake.

27:51.030 --> 27:51.720
My Lord.

27:51.810 --> 27:53.910
We've found out
General He's exact location.

27:53.910 --> 27:55.930
But Lincheng is Great Yong's territory.

27:55.930 --> 27:57.960
I'm afraid many in the Yong Army know you.

27:57.960 --> 27:59.920
The Black Eagle Army
is also stationed nearby.

27:59.920 --> 28:01.070
Our actions

28:01.570 --> 28:02.720
will easily attract attention.

28:02.720 --> 28:07.680
[Border between Great Yong and Great Yan]
[Prisoner of War Camp, Lincheng]

28:04.920 --> 28:06.120
Tomorrow, Great Yong

28:06.230 --> 28:08.680
will exchange prisoners of war
with Great Yan.

28:08.680 --> 28:10.160
They definitely won't let anything happen

28:10.160 --> 28:11.690
to He Xiao the night before.

28:11.830 --> 28:14.550
Xiao Ran only needs to set a fire
in the corner of the prisoner of war camp.

28:14.550 --> 28:16.680
He Xiao will definitely be relocated.

28:16.880 --> 28:17.590
Go!

28:17.670 --> 28:19.270
Hurry, go get water!

28:19.290 --> 28:19.900
All right.

28:21.960 --> 28:22.550
Let's go.

28:22.830 --> 28:23.790
Follow them

28:24.110 --> 28:26.350
and see where they'll move to.

28:30.680 --> 28:33.030
In 4 hours, when the sky is gray,

28:33.030 --> 28:35.160
people's minds will be least alert.

28:35.790 --> 28:38.480
I will go in and rescue He Xiao then.

28:39.030 --> 28:39.680
Xiao Ran,

28:40.310 --> 28:42.440
you wait outside the city to back us up.

28:42.590 --> 28:43.450
Fang Miaomiao,

28:43.880 --> 28:45.960
go to Baichuan Ferry and find a boat.

28:46.790 --> 28:48.070
We'll leave by water.

28:53.440 --> 28:55.770
A fire broke out
in the middle of the night.

28:56.300 --> 28:57.980
What the hell.

29:00.960 --> 29:01.820
Who do you want?

29:01.960 --> 29:03.160
If you want to live,

29:03.440 --> 29:05.770
take me
to the Commander of the Xiuli Army,

29:05.830 --> 29:06.830
He Xiao.

29:07.030 --> 29:07.680
You...

29:08.510 --> 29:09.720
Where exactly is he?

29:09.960 --> 29:10.550
He's...

29:11.550 --> 29:12.440
He's inside.

29:12.570 --> 29:13.960
If you dare lie to me,

29:14.510 --> 29:16.070
I will kill you on the spot.

29:16.640 --> 29:17.200
Go.

29:19.420 --> 29:20.640
Damn He Xiao.

29:20.840 --> 29:23.160
You killed so many
of our Great Yong people

29:23.160 --> 29:24.890
and still want to be exchanged?

29:25.930 --> 29:26.790
In your dreams!

29:27.160 --> 29:28.820
Even for a prisoner exchange,

29:28.880 --> 29:30.440
I'll cripple you first.

29:30.680 --> 29:32.280
When you return to Great Yan,

29:32.350 --> 29:34.810
you'll be a cripple
for the rest of your life.

29:38.240 --> 29:38.960
Inside.

29:47.260 --> 29:48.020
Where is he?

29:48.640 --> 29:49.400
Inside.

29:49.590 --> 29:50.750
He Xiao is inside.

30:00.590 --> 30:01.240
He Xiao.

30:02.200 --> 30:02.830
He Xiao.

30:18.360 --> 30:19.220
General Cheng,

30:19.750 --> 30:21.610
thanks for your timely reminder.

30:21.750 --> 30:22.720
Otherwise,

30:23.550 --> 30:25.880
we would have lost the key prisoner today.

30:28.020 --> 30:29.500
Put out the fire! Put out the fire!

30:29.090 --> 30:30.500
[4 hours ago]

30:29.840 --> 30:31.880
Lock all the prisoners
in the wooden cells!

30:31.880 --> 30:32.510
Hurry!

30:32.790 --> 30:33.550
Lord Liu.

30:33.790 --> 30:34.310
Hurry!

30:34.330 --> 30:35.060
Who's there?

30:35.270 --> 30:37.880
I'm Cheng Yuan,
Commander of Great Yan's Black Eagle Army.

30:37.880 --> 30:38.480
Coming!

30:39.310 --> 30:40.840
The official report states

30:41.440 --> 30:42.960
that the Great Yan general

30:43.050 --> 30:45.050
escorting the prisoners is Shi Yan.

30:45.110 --> 30:47.680
What is your purpose here, General Cheng?

30:47.680 --> 30:49.920
Lord Liu, you have such great composure.

30:49.920 --> 30:51.580
You can barely save yourself,

30:52.110 --> 30:53.640
yet you still care about me.

30:56.440 --> 30:57.370
What do you mean?

30:57.640 --> 31:00.720
Do you think this fire is a coincidence?

31:01.270 --> 31:02.930
If you move the prisoners now,

31:03.310 --> 31:05.310
you will fall into the enemy's trap.

31:05.480 --> 31:06.200
Chu Qiao,

31:07.240 --> 31:08.720
you can die in peace.

31:27.680 --> 31:28.290
Xing.

31:28.630 --> 31:29.430
Zhuge Yue?

31:29.690 --> 31:30.890
Kill Zhuge Yue for me!

31:51.100 --> 31:51.690
Go.

31:52.190 --> 31:53.270
Assassins!

32:07.070 --> 32:08.750
Hurry! Keep searching!

32:10.310 --> 32:10.880
Hurry!

32:17.400 --> 32:18.200
What's wrong?

32:19.090 --> 32:20.390
We have to split up.

32:20.480 --> 32:22.030
Otherwise, it'll be too conspicuous.

32:22.030 --> 32:23.000
You go that way.

32:23.000 --> 32:25.030
I'll take the main road ahead
to distract them.

32:25.030 --> 32:26.630
We'll meet outside Xicheng.

32:27.270 --> 32:27.880
Okay.

32:33.240 --> 32:35.480
Fang Miaomiao and the others
are at Baichuan Ferry.

32:35.480 --> 32:36.720
If you can't wait for me,

32:36.720 --> 32:37.960
we'll meet at the ferry.

32:37.960 --> 32:38.550
Okay.

32:43.470 --> 32:44.200
Don't worry.

32:44.620 --> 32:45.210
Go.

33:05.070 --> 33:06.130
Search carefully!

33:06.200 --> 33:07.400
Don't miss any clues!

33:07.400 --> 33:08.330
Find them for me!

33:08.350 --> 33:09.110
-Yes!
-Yes!

33:16.350 --> 33:17.030
Zhuge Yue!

33:18.680 --> 33:19.390
Zhuge Yue!

33:23.210 --> 33:23.900
Zhuge Yue!

33:25.790 --> 33:26.790
You are poisoned?

33:28.890 --> 33:29.750
There's movement over there.

33:29.750 --> 33:30.950
Everyone, follow me.

33:32.030 --> 33:32.470
Go.

33:32.960 --> 33:33.490
Hurry up.

33:40.310 --> 33:41.000
They are there.

33:41.000 --> 33:41.660
Chase them!

33:55.860 --> 33:57.030
Over there! Go!

34:08.110 --> 34:09.239
They are over there!

34:14.360 --> 34:14.960
Xing,

34:15.710 --> 34:16.230
you...

34:17.230 --> 34:18.000
Zhuge Yue,

34:18.710 --> 34:20.370
we will live and die together.

34:23.400 --> 34:24.060
Over there!

34:25.409 --> 34:26.150
Stop!

34:38.750 --> 34:39.750
Such a high cliff,

34:40.320 --> 34:41.630
they won't survive.

34:41.650 --> 34:42.510
Let's retreat.

34:48.760 --> 34:49.840
Why are you alone?

34:49.860 --> 34:50.520
Where is Princess Fu?

34:50.520 --> 34:51.360
She didn't show up.

34:51.360 --> 34:52.480
There's a curfew in the city.

34:52.480 --> 34:53.400
The Great Yong soldiers

34:53.400 --> 34:54.630
and the Black Eagle Army
are both searching for her.

34:54.630 --> 34:55.800
Why is the Black Eagle Army here?

34:55.800 --> 34:56.550
I don't know either.

34:56.550 --> 34:58.350
We must find a way to save her now.

34:58.590 --> 34:59.450
General Cheng.

35:02.670 --> 35:04.760
Does your wound hurt?

35:05.110 --> 35:06.670
I'll go get a physician for you.

35:06.670 --> 35:08.000
No need, Lord Liu.

35:08.510 --> 35:09.840
It's just a flesh wound.

35:09.840 --> 35:10.770
It won't kill me.

35:12.110 --> 35:14.110
I have some imperial medicine

35:14.630 --> 35:16.110
from the Great Yong Palace.

35:16.110 --> 35:17.920
Within 3 days of application,

35:18.110 --> 35:20.510
the wound will heal naturally.

35:21.030 --> 35:22.160
It's very precious.

35:25.000 --> 35:26.130
Thank you, Lord Liu.

35:26.550 --> 35:27.480
You're welcome.

35:28.030 --> 35:31.400
Thanks to your great help today,

35:31.400 --> 35:32.960
I didn't lose the key prisoner.

35:32.960 --> 35:35.670
I am deeply grateful.

35:42.280 --> 35:43.230
It's a pity

35:44.960 --> 35:46.320
that they escaped.

35:47.480 --> 35:48.190
Lord Liu.

35:48.960 --> 35:50.110
If you live,

35:50.710 --> 35:53.110
someone will know what happened tonight.

35:53.770 --> 35:54.550
Then I

35:55.280 --> 35:56.880
won't be able to live either.

36:21.740 --> 36:22.530
Chu,

36:22.740 --> 36:24.670
the law of the jungle
prevails in this world.

36:24.670 --> 36:26.470
There is no justice or fairness.

36:26.740 --> 36:27.380
Xing,

36:27.710 --> 36:29.040
to the ends of the earth,

36:29.280 --> 36:30.680
we live and die together.

36:30.920 --> 36:32.230
To the new King of Great Yan!

36:32.230 --> 36:32.920
Cheers!

36:34.000 --> 36:35.850
You kept saying you liked me!

36:35.880 --> 36:37.070
You liar!

36:39.370 --> 36:40.160
Remember,

36:40.350 --> 36:43.280
you are not allowed
to hide anything from me anymore.

36:44.530 --> 36:45.480
Kill her.
